SUMMARY:Cheese & Wine Pairing
DESCRIPTION:🧀🍷 Wine & Cheese Pairing Experience at Great Bear Vineyards 🍷🧀\nSunday\, March 29 | 12:00–3:00 pm \nIf wine and cheese are your love language\, this one’s for you. \nJoin us at Great Bear Vineyards for an afternoon of delicious discovery featuring a curated flight of four award-winning wines\, each thoughtfully paired with a premium artisan cheese designed to bring out the very best in both. It’s indulgent\, flavorful\, and dangerously easy to fall in love with every pairing. \n✨ Want to elevate your experience? \nAdd an exclusive behind-the-scenes barrel room tour\, where you’ll see our winemaking process up close and sample estate-grown wines straight from the barrel—a rare and memorable treat. \nThis experience is perfect whether you’re a devoted foodie\, a curious wine lover\, or simply in the mood for something delightfully decadent. You’ll get the chance to: \n• Savor the unique profiles of our handcrafted wines\n• Discover why certain cheeses make wines shine\n• Pick up fun\, easy pairing tips—or just relax and enjoy every bite and sip \nBring your favorite people and let the flavors unfold. The pairing offers a hearty\, satisfying tasting with a focus on flavor harmony. Additional wine and snacks will be available for purchase if you’d like to linger a little longer. \n🎟 Tickets required. Space is limited—come sip\, snack\, and savor with us!
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/cheese-wine-pairing/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards (Great Bear)\, 24800 County Rd 101A
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/3-29-26-Thumbnail.png
