SUMMARY:Davis Bookworms
DESCRIPTION:Do you love reading\, but hate being told what book to read? Are you intrigued by the idea of a book club\, but too busy to do the reading beforehand? If so\, then you’ll fit right in with the Davis Bookworms! We are a brand new “silent” book club\, in which everyone brings a book of their own choosing\, reads for an hour\, and then socializes for an hour. We meet every two weeks on Sunday at Nashoba Wines\, right here in Davis. So whether you’re feeling the Sunday Scaries\, or just love to read\, come join us for an afternoon of good books\, good wine\, and good company!
