SUMMARY:Watermelon Music Open Mic
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the third Open Mic of 2026! Whether you’re looking for a venue to share your own talents or just looking to enjoy hearing (and seeing) some local performers\, we invite you to this free monthly event. We provide the sound\, stage and lights – the rest is up to you. Play us your favorite song\, tell us some jokes\, act out a scene from your favorite play with friends. \nWe ask only that each performance be suitable for an all-ages venue\, and that you arrive on time and stay until the end to support your fellow performers. \nDoor open and sign-ups begin at 5:30. First act goes on at 6:00. We hope to see you here!
